<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?><feed xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" ><generator uri="https://jekyllrb.com/" version="3.7.4">Jekyll</generator><link href="http://localhost:4000/feed.xml" rel="self" type="application/atom+xml" /><link href="http://localhost:4000/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" /><updated>2020-07-07T21:42:20+08:00</updated><id>http://localhost:4000/feed.xml</id><title type="html">Weimode</title><subtitle>T.R.Y</subtitle><entry><title type="html">How to clear cache in WeChat browser</title><link href="http://localhost:4000/wechat/2018/04/11/clearCacheInWechat.html" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="How to clear cache in WeChat browser" /><published>2018-04-11T16:28:27+08:00</published><updated>2018-04-11T16:28:27+08:00</updated><id>http://localhost:4000/wechat/2018/04/11/clearCacheInWechat</id><content type="html" xml:base="http://localhost:4000/wechat/2018/04/11/clearCacheInWechat.html">&lt;p&gt;最近经常接触到需要在微信内置浏览器内打开的项目，常常为它的缓存机制感到头痛。&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;至于常用的头部“no-cache”在微信内置浏览器中并不好用&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;因此查询了相关文档，发现了一种很好用的方法：在页面URL中加上时间戳。&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;eg.&quot;https://baidu.com?v=(timestamp)&quot;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</content><author><name></name></author><summary type="html">最近经常接触到需要在微信内置浏览器内打开的项目，常常为它的缓存机制感到头痛。</summary></entry><entry><title type="html">Welcome</title><link href="http://localhost:4000/welcome/2018/03/22/welcome.html" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Welcome" /><published>2018-03-22T14:43:27+08:00</published><updated>2018-03-22T14:43:27+08:00</updated><id>http://localhost:4000/welcome/2018/03/22/welcome</id><content type="html" xml:base="http://localhost:4000/welcome/2018/03/22/welcome.html">&lt;p&gt;It is a joyful day for me!&lt;/p&gt;

